description:
Nair Easiwax Mini Wax Strips are designed to remove unwanted hair from the face and sensitive areas quickly and easily with long laster results.

Nair Easiwax Mini Wax Strips remove unwanted hair from the face and sensitive areas quickly and easily. With chamomile extract that require no preparation, these ready to use wax strips are easy, convenient and will leave your skin feeling smoother for longer. Made from high quality resin wax the strips are simply warmed between your palms in seconds and are reusable.

Removes hair as short as 3mm

Results that last up to 4 weeks

Wax is enriched with Chamomile extract

Cellophane strip for precise application

Dermatologically tested
name: Nair Hair Removal Wax Easiwax Mini Strips 20 Pack
